Title: One-loop effective action for Einstein gravity in special background

gaugeAuthors: P.M.Lavrov, A.A.Reshetnyak

Comments: 17 pages, Latex, no figures

Journal-ref: Phys. Lett. B351 (1995) 105

The one-loop effective action for Einstein gravity in a special one-parameterbackground gauge is calculated up to first order in a gauge parameter. It isshown that the effective action does not depend upon the gauge parameter onshell.